Arsenal May Exchange Nasri for Manchester City’s Tevez, Sun Says

-- B y   A m b e r e e n   C h o u d h u r y
-- 
2011-08-13T10:39:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-13/arsenal-may-exchange-nasri-for-manchester-city-s-tevez-sun-says.html
Arsenal Football Club may seek to
exchange midfield player Samir Nasri for Manchester City’s
unsettled striker  Carlos Tevez , the Sun newspaper said.  Nasri had hoped to sign with Manchester City yesterday in
an 180,000-pounds ($290,000) a-week deal, the newspaper said.
Tevez may be expecting wages of as much as 200,000 pounds a
week, the Sun said, without citing anyone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ambereen Choudhury in London at 
